			<p>These "Tools" are applications that can be run in-browser. Each page will have a form or interface to use the tool, no download required.</p>
            <p class="adj">Unlike my <a href="/projects/">Projects</a>, in most cases the source code will not be readily downloadable, and may be integrated into the site itself. You can try searching through the repository for this site if you want to see how something works.</p>
		</article>
